2000-04-23 11:46 +0000 [r727]  Marcin Bohosiewicz <marcus/at/pld-linux.org>

	* sysconfig/network-scripts/ifup,
	  sysconfig/network-scripts/ifup-ppp: * In ifup file added suppoer
